<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-advance-invoice.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">Create a sales order, or select an existing sales order. Click <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-advance-invoice.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">Invoice</strong>, and then click <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-advance-invoice.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">Generate</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-advance-invoice.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">Advance invoice</strong>. On the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-advance-invoice.md" sourcestartlinenumber="85">Create advance invoice</strong> page, set following fields.</p>
